WEBVTT

00:08:58.866 --> 00:09:02.439
and I think it is their
human right to remain so.

00:09:02.439 --> 00:09:04.862
Why are these the tribes
that hide from man?

00:09:04.862 --> 00:09:05.967
Here's why.

00:09:05.967 --> 00:09:09.225
Obviously, some of this 
was set off in 1492.

00:09:09.225 --> 00:09:11.247
But at the turn of the last century

00:09:11.247 --> 00:09:13.072
was the rubber trade.

00:09:13.072 --> 00:09:14.722
The demand for natural rubber,

00:09:14.722 --> 00:09:16.628
which came from the Amazon,

00:09:16.628 --> 00:09:19.802
set off the botanical
equivalent of a gold rush.

00:09:19.802 --> 00:09:21.678
Rubber for bicycle tires,

00:09:21.678 --> 00:09:23.296
rubber for automobile tires,

00:09:23.296 --> 00:09:25.047
rubber for zeppelins.

00:09:25.047 --> 00:09:28.054
It was a mad race to get that rubber,

00:09:28.054 --> 00:09:30.732
and the man on the left, Julio Arana,